OL,3,CWill Makerfield choose the next PM?
OL,5,FVoters in the Makerfield by-election
OL,6,Fcould have a major influence over the
OL,7,Fnext prime minister if they decide to
OL,8,Felect Andy Burnham as their new MP.
OL,10,FThe Greater Manchester by-election was
OL,11,Ftriggered by the resignation of
OL,12,FLabour's Josh Simons, who stood down
OL,13,Fto let Burnham attempt to win the seat
OL,14,Fand return to Westminster - ultimately
OL,15,Fto replace Sir Keir Starmer.
OL,17,FAhead of polling, the current Greater
OL,18,FManchester Mayor urged people to "vote
OL,19,Fto change politics" and vowed to take
OL,20,Fthe "fight as high as I can possibly
OL,21,Ftake it".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
