OL,3,CWill Makerfield choose the next PM?
OL,5,FWhat happens if Burnham wins?
OL,7,FThe Greater Manchester Mayor can
OL,8,Freturn to Parliament if he wins the
OL,9,Fseat, and has indicated he would put
OL,10,Fhimself forward in an expected
OL,11,Fchallenge to Starmer's leadership.
OL,13,FBurnham and his allies are reportedly
OL,14,Fhoping for a "coronation" in which
OL,15,FStarmer stands aside, rather than a
OL,16,Fleadership contest.
OL,18,FBut the prime minister has repeatedly
OL,19,Fmade it clear he has no intention of
OL,20,Fstanding down and says that he will
OL,21,Ffight any challenge to his leadership.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
