PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1781849901
OL,3,CWill Makerfield choose the next PM?
OL,5,FStarmer has said he is willing to
OL,6,Foffer the Mayor of Greater Manchester
OL,7,Fa "big" job in his Government, should
OL,8,FBurnham win when the votes are counted.
OL,10,FAllies of Burnham have said he was not
OL,11,Finterested in the offer, insisting
OL,12,F"the benefit Andy has is the wind of
OL,13,Fchange for not having been associated
OL,14,Fwith the Government's failings."
OL,16,FSpeaking to journalists at the G7
OL,17,Fsummit, Starmer warned Burnham to not
OL,18,Fchallenge him for leadership.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
