PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1781849901
OL,3,CWill Makerfield choose the next PM?
OL,5,FHe said that if Burnham wins the
OL,6,FMakerfield by-election, his focus
OL,7,Fshould instead be on helping the party
OL,8,Fwin the Manchester mayoralty again,
OL,9,Fcalling it "one of the biggest by-
OL,10,Felections that we've ever fought".
OL,12,FFellow leadership hopeful and former
OL,13,Fhealth secretary Wes Streeting is
OL,14,Freported to have met Mr Burnham while
OL,15,Fcampaigning in Makerfield on Monday,
OL,16,Fthough a source said "no deals were
OL,17,Fdone" as a result of the meeting.
OL,19,FA by-election for the mayoralty would
OL,20,Flikely to be at the end of July.
OL,26,@xD@VOUyD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
