OL,3,CWill Makerfield choose the next PM?
OL,5,FWhat happens if Burnham loses?
OL,7,FPolls have consistently predicted it
OL,8,Fwill be a race between Labour's and
OL,9,FReform UK's Robert Kenyon, a local
OL,10,Fplumber.
OL,12,FKenyon was born in the constituency
OL,13,Fand came second to Labour's Josh
OL,14,FSimmons in 2024.
OL,16,FThe party secured just under a third
OL,17,Fof the vote, placing Makerfield among
OL,18,FReform's strongest performances
OL,19,Fnationally.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
